<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Sanction Letter & Key Fact Statement</title>
    <style>
      /* --- KEEPING YOUR EXISTING CSS EXACTLY AS IT IS --- */
      .logos {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between; /* puts one left, one right */
        align-items: center;
        margin-bottom: 30px;
      }

      .logos img {
        max-width: 170px;
        height: auto;
      }

      * {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        box-sizing: border-box;
        font-size: 14px;
      }
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #333;
        background-color: #f5f5f5;
      }
      .document-container {
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 1000px; /* or 1200px */
        margin: 20px auto;
        background: white;
        padding: 40px;
      }

      .document-header {
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
        padding-bottom: 20px;
      }
      .document-header h1 {
        color: #2c3e50;
        font-size: 18px;
        font-weight: bold;
        letter-spacing: 1px;
      }
      .basic-info {
        margin-bottom: 25px;
      }
      .info-table {
        width: 100%;
        border-collapse: collapse;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }
      .info-table td {
        border: 1px solid #ddd;
        padding: 10px;
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 12px;
      }
      .info-table td:first-child {
        background-color: #f0f0f0;
        font-weight: bold;
      }
      .intro-text {
        margin-bottom: 25px;
        text-align: justify;
        font-size: 14px;
      }
      .intro-text p {
        margin-bottom: 15px;
        color: #555;
      }
      .loan-details h3,
      .loan-parameters h3,
      .contingent-charges h3,
      .other-disclosures h3,
      .repayment-schedule h3,
      .terms-conditions h3 {
        color: #2c3e50;
      }
      .details-table,
      .parameters-table {
        width: 100%;
        border-collapse: collapse;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }
      .details-table td,
      .parameters-table td {
        border: 1px solid #ddd;
        padding: 8px 12px;
        font-size: 13px;
      }
      .details-table td:first-child,
      .parameters-table td:first-child {
        width: 50px;
        text-align: center;
        font-weight: bold;
      }
      .details-table td:nth-child(2),
      .parameters-table td:nth-child(2) {
        width: 50%;
        font-weight: bold;
      }
      .details-table td:last-child,
      .parameters-table td:last-child {
        width: 40%;
      }
      .parameters-table th {
        background-color: #f0f0f0;
        color: #333333;
        padding: 12px;
        text-align: center;
        font-weight: bold;
        border: 1px solid #ddd;
      }
      .schedule-table {
        width: 100%;
        border-collapse: collapse;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }
      .schedule-table th,
      .schedule-table td {
        border: 1px solid #ddd;
        padding: 10px;
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 14px;
        background-color: white;
      }
      .schedule-table th {
        background-color: #f0f0f0;
        color: #333333;
        font-weight: bold;
      }
      .schedule-table tr:nth-child(even) {
        background-color: #f8f9fa;
      }
      .terms-conditions {
        margin-top: 30px;
      }
      .terms-conditions ol {
        margin-left: 20px;
        font-size: 14px;
      }
      .terms-conditions li {
        margin-bottom: 12px;
        text-align: justify;
        line-height: 1.5;
      }
      .terms-conditions ul {
        margin-left: 20px;
        margin-top: 8px;
      }
      .terms-conditions ul li {
        margin-bottom: 5px;
      }
      .acknowledgement {
        margin-top: 40px;
        padding-top: 20px;
      }
      .acknowledgement p {
        margin-bottom: 15px;
      }
      .signature-area {
        margin-top: 30px;
        text-align: left;
      }
      .signature-area p {
        margin-bottom: 10px;
        font-weight: bold;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="document-container">
      <div class="logos">
        <img
          src="https://nexiloans.s3.ap-south-1.amazonaws.com/logo.svg"
          alt="Nexiloans logo"
          class="logo-left"
        />
        <% if (lender_detail && lender_detail.lenderID === 2) { %>
          <img
            src="https://nexiloans.s3.ap-south-1.amazonaws.com/nandanvan.png"
            alt="New lender logo"
            class="logo-right"
          />
        <% } else { %>
          <img
            src="https://nexiloans.s3.ap-south-1.amazonaws.com/yashikLoans.png"
            alt="Yashik loans logo"
            class="logo-right"
          />
        <% } %>
        <!-- <img
          src="https://nexiloans.s3.ap-south-1.amazonaws.com/yashikLoans.png"
          alt="Yashik loans logo"
          class="logo-right"
        /> -->
      </div>
      <header class="document-header">
        <h1>SANCTION LETTER & KEY FACT STATEMENT</h1>
      </header>

      <section class="basic-info">
        <table class="info-table">
          <tr>
            <td>Date</td>
            <td>Name of R.E.</td>
            <td>Applicant Name</td>
            <td>Loan Number</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>
              <% if (approval_detail && approval_detail.createdDate) { %> <%=new Date(approval_detail.createdDate).toLocaleDateString('en-GB')%> <% } else { %> <%= new Date().toLocaleDateString('en-GB') %> <%} %>
            </td>
            <td>
              <% if (lender_detail && lender_detail.lender_display_name) { %><%= lender_detail.lender_display_name %> <% } else { %> Yashik Finlease Private Limited <% } %>
            </td>
              <td>
              <% if (customer_detail && (customer_detail.customerName || customer_detail.name)) { %> <%= customer_detail.customerName || customer_detail.name %> <% } else { %> N/A <% } %>
            </td>
            <td>
              <%= (loan_detail && loan_detail.loanNo) ? loan_detail.loanNo : "N/A" %>
            </td>
          </tr>
        </table>
      </section>

      <section class="intro-text">
        <p>
          <strong>
            M/s. <%= (lender_detail && lender_detail.lender_display_name) ? lender_detail.lender_display_name : "Yashik Finlease Private Limited" %>
          </strong>
          ("Lender/ R.E.") is pleased to inform you ("Borrower") that you are
          eligible for a loan facility, subject to the terms and conditions set
          out herein.
        </p>
        <p>
          The Loan is being facilitated through the technology platform of <strong>M/s. Nexi Fintech Private Limited</strong> ("Lending Service Provider" or "LSP"), pursuant to an arrangement between <%= (lender_detail && lender_detail.lender_display_name) ? lender_detail.lender_display_name : "Yashik Finlease Private Limited" %> and Nexi Fintech Private Limited.
        </p>
        <p>
          We are pleased to communicate the <em>in-principal</em> sanction of
          the loan facility, the details of which are set forth below:
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="loan-details">
        <h3>Key Loan Terms</h3>
        <table class="details-table">
          <tr>
            <td>1</td>
            <td>Lender</td>
            <td>
              <%= (lender_detail && lender_detail.lender_display_name) ? lender_detail.lender_display_name : "Yashik Finlease Private Limited" %>
            </td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>2</td>
            <td>LSP</td>
            <td>Nexi Fintech Private Limited</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>3</td>
            <td>Proposal Validity</td>
            <td>5 days</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>4</td>
            <td>Application ID</td>
            <td>
              <%= (lead_detail && lead_detail.leadID) ? lead_detail.leadID : "N/A" %>
            </td>
          </tr>

          <tr>
            <td>5</td>
            <td><h3>Applicant Details</h3></td>
            <td></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td></td>
            <td>Name</td>
            <td>
              <% if (customer_detail && (customer_detail.customerName || customer_detail.name)) { %> <%= customer_detail.customerName || customer_detail.name %> <% } else { %> N/A <% } %>
            </td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td></td>
            <td>Address</td>
            <td>
              <% if (address && address.address) { %> <%= address.address %> <% } else { %> N/A <% } %>
            </td>
          </tr>

          <tr>
            <td></td>
            <td>PAN</td>
            <td>
              <%= (customer_detail && customer_detail.pancard) ? customer_detail.pancard : "N/A" %>
            </td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td></td>
            <td>Aadhaar</td>
            <td>
              XXXX-XXXX-<%= (customer_detail && customer_detail.aadharNo) ? customer_detail.aadharNo : "N/A" %>
            </td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td></td>
            <td>Date Of Birth</td>
            <td>
              <%= (customer_detail && customer_detail.dob) ? new Date(customer_detail.dob).toLocaleDateString('en-GB') : "N/A" %>
            </td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td></td>
            <td>Mobile</td>
            <td>
              <% if (customer_detail && (customer_detail.mobileNo || customer_detail.mobile)) { %> <%= customer_detail.mobileNo || customer_detail.mobile %> <% } else { %> N/A <% } %>
            </td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td></td>
            <td>Email</td>
            <td>
              <% if (customer_detail && (customer_detail.email || customer_detail.emailId)) { %> <%= customer_detail.email || customer_detail.emailId %> <% } else { %> N/A <% } %>
            </td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>6</td>
            <td>Purpose</td>
            <td>
              <%= (lead_detail && lead_detail.purpose) ? lead_detail.purpose : "N/A" %>
            </td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>7</td>
            <td><h3>Disbursement Through Bank Transfer</h3></td>
            <td></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td></td>
            <td>Bank Name</td>
            <td>
              <%= (account_detail && account_detail.bank_name) ? account_detail.bank_name : "N/A" %>
            </td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td></td>
            <td>IFSC Code</td>
            <td>
              <%= (account_detail && account_detail.ifsc) ? account_detail.ifsc : "N/A" %>
            </td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td></td>
            <td>Account Number</td>
            <td>
              <%= (account_detail && account_detail.account_number) ? account_detail.account_number : "N/A" %>
            </td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>8</td>
            <td>Tenure (in Days)</td>
            <td>
              <%= (approval_detail && approval_detail.tenure) ? approval_detail.tenure : "N/A" %>
            </td>
          </tr>
        </table>
      </section>

      <section class="loan-parameters">
        <h3>Financial Terms</h3>
        <table class="parameters-table">
          <tr>
            <th>Sr. No.</th>
            <th>Parameters</th>
            <th>Amount (₹)</th>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>(i)</td>
            <td>Loan Sanctioned</td>
            <td>
              <%= (approval_detail && approval_detail.loanAmtApproved) ? approval_detail.loanAmtApproved : "N/A" %>
            </td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>(ii)</td>
            <td>Total Interest Payable</td>
            <td><%= intem ? Math.round(intem) : "N/A" %></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>(iii)</td>
            <td>Processing Fees</td>
            <td>
              <%= (approval_detail && approval_detail.adminFee) ? Math.round(approval_detail.adminFee) : "NIL" %>
            </td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>(iv)</td>
            <td>Net Disbursement ((i)-(iii))</td>
            <td><%= fdb ? Math.round(fdb) : "N/A" %></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>(v)</td>
            <td>Total Amount Payable by Borrower ((i)+(ii))</td>
            <td><%= rep1 ? Math.round(rep1) : "N/A" %></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>(vi)</td>
            <td>Interest Rate Per day (%)</td>
            <td>
              <%= (approval_detail && approval_detail.roi) ? approval_detail.roi : "N/A" %>
            </td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>(vii)</td>
            <td>Annual Percentage Rate (APR)%</td>
            <td><%= apr ? apr.toFixed(2) : "N/A" %></td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>(viii)</td>
            <td>Tenure (in Days)</td>
            <td>
              <%= (approval_detail && approval_detail.tenure) ? approval_detail.tenure : "N/A" %>
            </td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>(ix)</td>
            <td>No. of Instalments</td>
            <td>1</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>(x)</td>
            <td>Instalment Amount</td>
            <td><%= rep1 ? Math.round(rep1) : "N/A" %></td>
          </tr>
        </table>
      </section>

      <section class="contingent-charges">
        <h3>Contingent Charges</h3>
        <table class="parameters-table">
          <tr>
            <td>1</td>
            <td>Penal charges for delay in payments of dues</td>
            <td>₹100 per day for the delay</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>2</td>
            <td>NACH/e-Mandate Bounce Charges</td>
            <td>₹500 + GST</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>3</td>
            <td>Statement of Account (SOA) Charges</td>
            <td>Nil</td>
          </tr>
        </table>
      </section>

      <section class="other-disclosures">
        <h3>Other Disclosures</h3>
        <table class="parameters-table">
          <tr>
            <td>1</td>
            <td>Cooling-off / Look-up Period</td>
            <td>3 days</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>2</td>
            <td>
              Details of LSP acting as recovery agent and authorized to approach
              the borrower
            </td>
            <td>Nexi Fintech Private Limited</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>3</td>
            <td>
              Name, designation, address and phone number of nodal grievance
              redressal officer designated specifically to deal with FinTech/
              digital lending related complaints/ issues
            </td>
            <td>
              <strong>Name :Mr.Karan Singh</strong><br />
              <strong>Designation: Manager (Compliance)</strong><br />
              <strong
                >Address: 410, Enkay Center, A Wing, Udyog Vihar, Phase-V,
                Gurugram, Haryana-122016</strong
              ><br />
              <strong>Email : karan.singh@nexiloans.com</strong>
            </td>
          </tr>
        </table>
      </section>

      <section class="repayment-schedule">
        <h3>Repayment Schedule (Tentative)</h3>
        <table class="schedule-table">
          <tr>
            <th>Instalment No.</th>
            <th>Principal (₹)</th>
            <th>Interest (₹)</th>
            <th>Instalment (₹)</th>
            <th>Due Date</th>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>One</td>
            <td>
              <%= (approval_detail && approval_detail.loanAmtApproved) ? approval_detail.loanAmtApproved : "N/A" %>
            </td>
            <td><%= intem ? Math.round(intem) : "N/A" %></td>
            <td><%= rep1 ? Math.round(rep1) : "N/A" %></td>
            <td>
              <%= (approval_detail && approval_detail.repayDate) ? new Date(approval_detail.repayDate).toLocaleDateString('en-GB') : "N/A" %>
            </td>
          </tr>
        </table>
      </section>

      <section class="terms-conditions">
        <h3>General Terms & Conditions</h3>
        <ol>
          <li>
            This Sanction Letter is issued on the basis of documents and
            details submitted by the Applicant. In the event of any discrepancy,
            the Lender reserves the right to revoke this sanction.
          </li>
          <li>
            The disbursement of the sanctioned loan is subject to:
            <ul>
              <li>
                - Execution and acceptance of the Loan Agreement, which shall
                supersede this Sanction Letter in case of conflict.
              </li>
              <li>
                - Borrower's express consent to the tenure, interest rate, and
                terms specified herein.
              </li>
            </ul>
          </li>
          <li>
            The Lender shall have the right to revoke this sanction if it is
            not accepted within five (5) days from the date of issuance.
          </li>
          <li>
            APR has been computed as the effective annualized interest rate
            on the net disbursed amount, using the IRR (Internal Rate of Return)
            approach.
          </li>
          <li>
            Within the Cooling-off Period, the Borrower may prepay the loan
            principal without incurring any prepayment penalty. Post this
            period, prepayment charges shall apply.
          </li>
          <li>
            In the event of default, the Lender and/or the Reserve Bank of
            India (RBI) and/or Credit Information Companies (CICs) may publish
            the Borrower's name as a defaulter, at their sole discretion.
          </li>
          <li>
            The Borrower hereby consents to the Lender disclosing and sharing
            their personal and financial information with RBI, CICs,
            professional advisors, affiliates, service providers, and any other
            agency authorized under applicable law.
          </li>
          <li>For more information, Please visit the link below:</li>
          <li>
            <a href="https://nexiloans.com/PrivacyPolicy"
              >https://nexiloans.com/PrivacyPolicy</a
            >
          </li>
        </ol>
      </section>

      <section class="acknowledgement">
        <br />
        <h3><strong>Acknowledgement</strong></h3>
        <p>
          <% if (customer_detail && (customer_detail.customerName || customer_detail.name)) { %> I, <%= customer_detail.customerName || customer_detail.name %>, hereby acknowledge that I have read, understood, and accepted the terms and conditions specified herein and in the Loan Proposal. <% } else { %> I, (Name of borrower), hereby acknowledge that I have read, understood, and accepted the terms and conditions specified herein and in the Loan Proposal. <% } %>
        </p>
        <div class="signature-area">
          <p>
            Acknowledgement Date: <%= new Date().toLocaleDateString('en-GB') %>
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
